author: Mrs Mladenka Hooper
title: Mrs Mladenka Hooper
text: Easy to order, quick delivery, great service. Nice little touches like pen. One negative issue was that it didn't fit quite right. All the dimensions were right but only 5 mm lower ment that my fan could not spin. Slightly annoying but with little stretch and adjustment it seems ok now. Works perfectly well. Excellent value. Thank you
